rComments: What a wonderful teacher and person.  He is a great pedagogue, but also really interesting and funny as a person.  He loves what he does and puts a lot of effort wanting us to succeed.  If you have the chance, take one of his classes!

Ah!  What can I say about Professor Barajas?  First of all, he is a great professor!  He is very helpful and very approachable.  I learnt so much in his class.  I was eager to go to each one of his class. Continue on teaching Professor Barajas!  Continue on doing a great work!
very good professor. bilingual. makes sure you understand every new concept. one thing you should know: always ask him about assignment deadlines and criterion.
Awesome class. It was nice a nice break, going to a very laid back class instead of the usual boring lecture from other profs.
Very friendly, tries to talk to everyone. Very helpful in class. Also, very cute!
seriously made me want to take spanish for years to come! so helpful, easy on the eyes, but sadly not everyone is like him teaching these classes.

The prof is very interesting, friendly and always there to help. Unlike most profs, he wants to get to know the names of all student in his class.
